  m_text: "</size> How to use Switch Board <size=60%> \n\n\nStatic Mode\n\nMode where
    Pickup is disabled. Moves to the nearest specified SwitchHolder to the player.\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPickup
    Mode\n\nMode where Pickup is enabled. You can call the SwitchBoard by Interacting
    with the holder."
